02078, 00000, "invalid setting for ALTER SYSTEM FIXED_DATE"
// *Cause:
// *Action:
//
02079, 00000, "no new sessions may join a committing distributed transaction"
// *Cause: A call to UPI2BG was issued in a session for a transaction that
