// *Action: Replace any LOG_ARCHIVE_DEST and LOG_ARCHIVE_DUPLEX_DEST
//          parameters with LOG_ARCHIVE_DEST_n (n = 1...10) parameters.
16031, 00000, "parameter %s destination string exceeds %s character limit"
