16063, 00000, "remote archival is enabled by another instance"
// *Cause:  Remote archival of database REDO log files has been enabled 
//          by another instance, and cannot be disabled for this instance.
// *Action: Set the REMOTE_ARCHIVE_ENABLE parameter to TRUE and restart 
