// *Action: Specify a correct value for parameter LOG_ARCHIVE_MIN_SUCCEED_DEST.
//          If the archive log parameters LOG_ARCHIVE_DEST or
//          LOG_ARCHIVE_DUPLEX_DEST are in use, set parameter
